Package ssmc

Class Attribute

java.lang.Object
ssmc.Attribute
public class Attribute
extends java.lang.Object
This Class defines this Attribute object. This object is used to store data from ASTNodes when visited.
Author:
AndrewCMoore

    • setModifier

      public void setModifier​(int i)
      This method is used to set the modifier in most cases. The Integer i is used in the method getModifier in class CAMValues. This returns an ArrayList of Strings that represent the modifiers of the method.
      Parameters:
      i - Integer representing an ASTNode's modifiers.

    • setModifier

      public void setModifier​(java.util.ArrayList<java.lang.String> modifier)
      This method is used to set the modifier in special cases, such as enumeration objects where the modifier is not automatically set by the system and must be set to "public static final"
      Parameters:
      modifier - an ArrayList of String values

    • setUsage

      public void setUsage​(int usage)
      This method allows the usage of an Attribute object to be hard reset.
      Parameters:
      usage - Integer value based on the number of times the attribute was used in the program.
